lead_paragraph: For all his heavy metal tennis, big-serving Milos Raonic relies on a quiet head on his shoulders during times of trouble, as was the case when beating Stanislas Wawrinka in the Australian Open fourth round on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Uses Inner Calm to Fend Off Wawrinka
headline.main: Raonic Uses Inner Calm to Fend Off Wawrinka
